Package pacman.models.maze

Contains model classes for each of the elements of the game maze.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BarObstacle
    Model for the obstacles on the map.
    Cookie
    Model for the cookies on the map.
    Maze
    Model for the maze and organising its components.
